# CurveLens Silver cron template — intentionally non-executable.
#
# Silver is experimental. Do not register or enable schedules from this file.
# A future reviewed schedule must create an isolated agent turn with:
#
#   CCVM_PRODUCT=silver
#   # data defaults automatically to ccvm/data/products/silver
#
# It must read AGENTS.md plus deployments/silver/AGENTS.md, acquire and verify
# the exact Section 64 bulletin, and invoke `$curvelens-daily-analysis` for its
# internal trade date. It must resume persisted state, perform no delivery by
# default, and ship disabled for explicit approval. A bare Python cron is
# unsupported.
